"src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24958,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/05\/prophet-oath-turner-hearts\/","url_meta":{"origin":33050,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Oaths: I swear by the turner of the hearts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The oath of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was, \u201cNo, by the turner of the hearts!\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6253 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0648\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0642\u064e\u0644\u0651\u0650\u0628\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0628\u0650 6253 \u0635\u062d\u064a\u062d \u0627\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3156,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/09\/swearing-oath-shirk\/","url_meta":{"origin":33050,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Oaths: Swearing by other than Allah an act of idolatry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever swears by other than Allah has committed an act of idolatry.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3251 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani Ibn Abi al-'Izz said, \"If one's swearing by other than Allah is intended to adjure\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7326,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/30\/umar-learns-to-love-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":33050,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Umar learns to love the Prophet more","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 30, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Hisham reported: We were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he was holding the hand of Umar ibn al-Khattab. Umar said to him, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, you are more beloved to me than everything but myself.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cNo, by\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37867,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/12\/swear-by-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33050,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Oaths: Swear by Allah and tell the truth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSwear your oaths by Allah, be righteous, and tell the truth. Verily, Allah Almighty loves for oaths to be sworn by Him.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 7\/267 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u00a0\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14369,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/21\/abandon-oath-better-option\/","url_meta":{"origin":33050,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Taqwa: Abandon oaths if more Godfearing option available","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Adi ibn Hatim reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever has given an oath by his right hand, then he sees something more righteous to Allah than it, let him choose righteousness.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1651 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u062f\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33050","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/da